  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (W-EP-03 stale input data)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. COU2 evaluates whether the computational model can predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. A model revision was issued in early 2026 to correct impeller geometry parameterisation; the primary rheological dataset used to calibrate blood viscosity inputs was collected under the prior model build (Q4 2025) and has not yet been re-validated against the updated geometry. Re-validation against the revised model is planned for Q2 2026 but no updated dataset has been ingested. All 13 credibility factors are assessed; achieved levels remain below required levels for seven factors.",
