    "type": "DecisionRecord",
    "actor": "https://uofa.net/synth/actor/morrison-credibility-lead",
    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "The credibility assessment team accepted the simulation package on the basis that the achieved credibility levels, while below required levels for seven of thirteen factors, are considered sufficient for the current regulatory submission phase. The team noted that the rheological calibration dataset predates the January 2026 model revision and that re-validation is planned for Q2 2026; this gap was assessed as tolerable given the conservative hemolysis threshold applied. The decision is conditional on completion of the re-validation prior to final regulatory submission.",
